    • Field Detail

      • lazyLoading

        public final CompletableFuture<Void> lazyLoading
        A CompletableFuture that completes once lazy loading was finished.

        Lazy loading is calling requestLanguages() and requestCategories() on API construction.

      • waitForLazyLoading

        public CodeBottle waitForLazyLoading()
        Waits for lazy loading to finish using CompletableFuture.join(). This method is intended to be used for API chaining, otherwise it is recommended to wait for lazyLoading yourself.
        Returns:
        this CodeBottle instance.
